description: Demolition of 1-43 Holyhead Close; refurbishment, including cladding, of three tower blocks, and sub-division of larger flats therein to increase total from 276 to 296 units. New development of 363 units of housing for sale and for rent, in blocks up to 6 storeys high, on land within the estate including designated housing amenity land. The proposal will include a new access road and a new community centre, with associated parking and landscaping.  N.B. Amended drawings and supporting documents
